MojoX-Renderer-XSLT

This module is used to extend Mojo / Mojolicious so XSLT templates can be rendered to the client.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc MojoX::Renderer::XSLT

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=MojoX-Renderer-XSLT

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/MojoX-Renderer-XSLT

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/MojoX-Renderer-XSLT

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/MojoX-Renderer-XSLT/


